Package: tidytopics
Type: Package
Title: Tidy Topic Modeling Toolbox for R
Version: 0.0.4
Author: Mans Magnusson
Maintainer: Mans Magnusson <mons.magnusson@gmail.com>
Description: Package to use for topic modeling in R in the tidy data framework of tidytext, tidyr and dplyr. The packag is based on dplyr data structures to improve performance.
